<li>Extensive testing in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge</li>
<li>Polyfills for newer JavaScript features</li>
<li>Vendor prefixes for experimental CSS properties</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="future-enhancements">Future Enhancements</h2>
<p>Future plans for this portfolio include:</p>
<ol>
<li>Adding a blog section for tech articles</li>
<li>Implementing dark/light theme toggle</li>
<li>Creating more interactive project showcases</li>
<li>Adding animations with GSAP or Framer Motion</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="lessons-learned">Lessons Learned</h2>
<p>This project reinforced the importance of:</p>
<ul>
<li>Planning component structure before implementation</li>
<li>Maintaining a clear separation of concerns</li>
<li>Optimizing assets for performance</li>
<li>Creating an intuitive user experience</li>
