<p>The application includes an interactive map that visualizes temperature, precipitation, and wind patterns:</p>
<p><img src="/images/projects/weather-app-map.jpg" alt="Weather Interactive Map"></p>
<p>This feature was implemented using the Leaflet.js library with custom layers for weather data:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// Weather map component
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="kr">import</span> <span class="nx">React</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nx">useEffect</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">useRef</span> <span class="p">}</span> <span class="nx">from</span> <span class="s1">&#39;react&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kr">import</span> <span class="nx">L</span> <span class="nx">from</span> <span class="s1">&#39;leaflet&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kr">import</span> <span class="s1">&#39;leaflet/dist/leaflet.css&#39;</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kr">const</span> <span class="nx">WeatherMap</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">({</span> <span class="nx">center</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">zoom</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">layers</span> <span class="p">})</span> <span class="p">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="kr">const</span> <span class="nx">mapRef</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">useRef</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">null</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="kr">const</span> <span class="nx">mapInstanceRef</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">useRef</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">null</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nx">useEffect</span><span class="p">(()</span> <span class="p">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="nx">mapInstanceRef</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">current</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="c1">// Initialize map
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span>      <span class="nx">mapInstanceRef</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">current</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">L</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">map</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">mapRef</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">current</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">setView</span><span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">[</span><span class="nx">center</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">lat</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">center</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">lon</span><span class="p">],</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">zoom</span> <span class="o">||</span> <span class="mi">10</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="p">);</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="c1">// Add base tile layer
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span>      <span class="nx">L</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">tileLayer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">attribution</span><span class="o">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&amp;copy; OpenStreetMap contributors&#39;</span>
